Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,CN,,0,0,0,,—————————OP—————————
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:34.20,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(250,180)}知道了如何變強的理由
